OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1772572323
OL,3,CCitizens Advice warn of loss of
OL,4,Cservices and jobs following council
OL,5,Cbudget cuts
OL,7,FA Citizens Advice in the South of
OL,8,FScotland has warned services and jobs
OL,9,Fare at risk, following council budget
OL,10,Fcuts.
OL,12,FIt was decided by Dumfries and
OL,13,FGalloway Council at a budget meeting
OL,14,Fthat its contract with Citizens Advice
OL,15,Fin Dumfries will be reduced by 20%.
OL,17,FThe organisation helps around 8,000
OL,18,Fclients annually - many who are often
OL,19,Fin vulnerable situations.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
